  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707230/extras/c02f46109c5914646e5a073086b51d67.avif?t=1511991338\" width=615 height=346 /></span><br><br>Prison Chainball Massacre is a fast paced, mindless arcade brawler set in a prison arena where you must fight incoming waves of enemies by using (or abusing) a unique and addictive physics based combat.<br><br>HOW TO PLAY:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707230/extras/4e4e4e1365eaaa356b8b36e33f0479ab.poster.avif?t=1511991338\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707230/extras/4e4e4e1365eaaa356b8b36e33f0479ab.webm?t=1511991338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707230/extras/4e4e4e1365eaaa356b8b36e33f0479ab.mp4?t=1511991338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SWING</strong> yourself around while a massive Chainball around your ankle crushes the corrupt prison guards!<br><strong>LOOT </strong> their hard earned money from the ground!<br><strong>UNLOCK UPGRADES</strong>, power ups, and customization for your character!<br><strong>COMPETE </strong>with other players on <strong>Steam Leaderboards!</strong><br><br>Stop wasting your time reading this and go play the game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707230/extras/c486d926c21e5c13fcf2665cd894b5aa.poster.avif?t=1511991338\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707230/extras/c486d926c21e5c13fcf2665cd894b5aa.webm?t=1511991338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://share